metadata.name: Smoke of Devastation
metadata.description:
Aftermath of a great war by great Commander Cyborg. who stood tall afer execution of almost entire race of humans. The smoke here is representing the end of the greatest living biengs ever which is due to creation of real artificial intelligance.
